org.eclipse.californium.core.observe

Class ObserveRelation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.californium.core.observe.ObserveRelation

  • public class ObserveRelation
extends Object
    The ObserveRelation is a server-side control structure. It represents a relation between a client endpoint and a resource on this server.
